Calculated fields and derived columns

ðŸš€ Outcome

This dashboard provides a clear, interactive view of sales performance and can be used by business stakeholders to:

Improve inventory planning

Optimize marketing timing

Focus on high-value products and regions

Support data-driven decision-making
